Ask HN: Where should I consider moving?
text:
Howdy HN,

I’m sure I’m not the only person considering leaving the US in the near future, but I’m struggling to make a short list of countries to explore.

I have friends that are starting the process for New Zealand, but their tech industry looks to be almost exclusively consulting driven. If like to end up at a place that’s more traditional. So where in the world should I look at?

Thank you!

title: Ask HN: On Beyond Error 33?
text: We all know of Catch 22 and Error 33 (https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Error_33). And I’ve heard of what I’ll here dub “Error 11”, i.e., making a project with a deadline depend upon one without a deadline. What other error xx’s do you know of (or propose)?

Ask HN: After KeyBase buyout by Zoom what do you use?
text:
I have not been keeping up with the latest chat applications, I really enjoyed KeyBase and was really, really hoping they would release @keybase emails next, with paid storage, and become yet another encrypted email option.

I have not seen much from them since the buyout in their blog, I can only assume it is basically abandonware at this point. It would be nice if they open sourced more of their infrastructure.
